title: Google\Cloud\Dataproc\V1\InstantiateInlineWorkflowTemplateRequest
name: InstantiateInlineWorkflowTemplateRequest
description:
A request to instantiate an inline workflow template.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.dataproc.v1.InstantiateInlineWorkflowTemplateRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The "resource name" of the workflow template region, as described in https://cloud.google.com/apis/design/resource_names of the form projects/{project_id}/regions/{region}

params.name: data.request_id
params.description: Optional. A tag that prevents multiple concurrent workflow instances with the same tag from running. This mitigates risk of concurrent instances started due to retries. It is recommended to always set this value to a UUID. The tag must contain only letters (a-z, A-Z), numbers (0-9), underscores (_), and hyphens (-). The maximum length is 40 characters.
